<%- include ('./partials/header-content') -%>
<main>
  <section>
    <h2>Example Usages</h2>
    <div class="subsection">
      <h3>Get Location for Your IP Address</h3>
      <p>To get the coordinates for your IP address, go to the route:</p>
      <pre>
        <code class="api-link">https://autumnchris-ip-location-api.onrender.com/api/ip/me</code>
        <button type="button" class="button copy-button api-my-ip" title="Copy to clipboard" aria-label="copy to clipboard"><span class="copy-icon far fa-copy"></span></button>
      </pre>
    </div>
    <div class="subsection">
      <h3>Get Location for a Custom IP Address</h3>
      <p>To get the coordinates for a custom IP address, change the last parameter to said IP address. For example, if I wanted to get the coordinates for the IP address, <code>72.14.192.0</code>, I would go to the route:</p>
      <pre>
        <code class="api-link">https://autumnchris-ip-location-api.onrender.com/api/ip/72.14.192.0</code>
        <button type="button" class="button copy-button api-custom-ip" title="Copy to clipboard" aria-label="copy to clipboard"><span class="copy-icon far fa-copy"></span></button>
      </pre>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
